### Content Alignment for Technical Precision
```css
/* Center-aligned for key insights */
.center-emphasis {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  height: 100%;
}

/* Left-aligned for detailed technical content */
.technical-detail {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 2rem;
}
```

### Custom Layout Classes for Research Presentations
```css
.algorithm-slide {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.results-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}

.timeline-slide {
  position: relative;
  padding-left: 3rem;
}
```

### Image Size Control for Technical Diagrams
```markdown
![width:500px height:300px](architecture.jpg)  <!-- Exact dimensions -->
![width:80%](results-table.png)                <!-- Relative sizing -->
![bg cover](methodology.jpg)                   <!-- Full slide background -->
![bg contain](equation.png)                    <!-- Fit within slide -->
```

### Header/Footer for Academic Branding
```markdown
---
header: 'Paper Title | Conference 2024'
footer: 'Author Name | Institution | Page'
---
```

```css
header, footer {
  position: absolute;
  left: 50px;
  right: 50px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
header {
  top: 20px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
}
footer {
  bottom: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}
```
